being attacked by a rather angry black man, and I did not have to raise a
finger, did not have to brandish a weapon. I know that this is rare, however by
not making myself a victim in the first place gave me the confidence to defuse
the situation without resorting to arms. If things had escalated I would have
been able to meet the level of escalation, and that confidence helped me.

