I have no problem with where this is leading.  If we do not end up with
two Harvey's, then I am not worried about one being destroyed later.
Any connection of the old and new body that transfers data or atoms from
the old to the new, building a new body while the old one is used up,
sounds like a perfect description of uploading to me.

